      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IMPERIAL AUDREY (7) doesn't win out of turn but recent form sound. Filled a minor placings again last time when second (30.65) at this track making it three placings in a row. The form from her last run stacks up well. Leading chance again. MR. SPECKLE (1) missed the frame last time when fourth (23.53) at The Gardens but prior to that had seven placings in a row. Goes very well here at the trip finding the frame in each of six starts. Comes through a solid form race last start. Likely to be about the money. DREAMS COME TRUE (2) has been hard to follow lately, running fourth (20.64) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Can improve sharply here. TRAIN TICKET (6) was unplaced here last start but gets his chance to atone.",
